#OpenFOAM mesh - wall resolving

This is a lowRE model

The variables q and Zeta are equivalent to k and epsilon.
The solver will automatically do the conversion from k and epsilon to q and Zeta
Define epsilon and k zero at the walls.
This model uses a value of dissipation zero at the walls in a natural way, does not require mathematical manipulation as in the KE model


#NOTE
Tu = 1%
Eddy vis. ratio = 1
